{"tid":2129050,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日出街差啲俾mk仔打 好彩有兩個靚女幫我解圍","createTime":"2020-07-28T10:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T14:52:27.000Z","uid":218575,"like":55,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca17334d165fba961afe3cb4c3fac424b7d5dd9","tid":2129050,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"行行下唔小心踩到個mk仔隻鞋甩咗<br />\n佢發曬癲咁屌鳩我 <br />\n我驚得濟係咁道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地染曬金毛咁一堆人<br />\n睇個款都係新技安個啲人<br />\n最後佢地話要我奶乾淨佢地隻鞋先放我走<br />\n唔知係咪太大聲 引咗好多人圍觀<br />\n有兩個靚女行咗過黎 <br />\n大大聲講咗句 <br />\n有無人性架 弱智嘅你地都恰就拉走咗我<br />\n好多謝個兩位絲打<br />\n<br />\n但我智力正常的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6691dd8314ec2cc3dc85760e4bb2bb35dd691370","tid":2129050,"uid":343964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:37:59.000Z","msg":"唔洗多謝我<br />\n轉返錢俾我就ok"},{"pid":"6bb9e79722d769a4e23983e5e59afa1f81688f9a","tid":2129050,"uid":121291,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"我我係隔離見到以為你真係弱智<br />\n原來唔係 sor"},{"pid":"1a869ddca3507d5ad7528271eecf8f8094f26067","tid":2129050,"uid":86813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"MK仔正一電子鴨黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連弱智都恰可恥"},{"pid":"8d36fc7cc479b78849baaaff562d610fd36d8d17","tid":2129050,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899c38dcb49b8b84c55d2ec7a554e942e6474f46","tid":2129050,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"邊個恰我老4肥bb"},{"pid":"c07af6771c0a27995c96a6a34d647ff366459c81","tid":2129050,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"899c38dc